welcome to the laboratory for scientific computing (lsc)!

the lsc is an interdisciplinary laboratory dedicated to research in
high-performance computing for scientific and engineering
applications.  the links on this page will lead you to information
about ongoing projects in the lab, people in the lab, and lab
facilities.


feel free to surf wherever you like and to download whatever interests
you.  some of the information is only of interest to people associated
with the lab, but everything is open to the world.


 for further information, contact:


  laboratory for scientific computing 
 department of computer science and engineering
